# 🛒 Quick Basket – Online Grocery Shopping Website

Quick Basket is a full-stack web-based grocery shopping platform that allows users to browse products, add items to their cart, and place orders easily. The project focuses on providing a smooth and user-friendly online shopping experience.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🛍️ Browse grocery products easily  
- ➕ Add to cart functionality  
- 🧾 Simple checkout system  
- 📱 Responsive design (mobile-friendly)  
- ⚡ Fast and smooth UI  
- 🗄️ MySQL database integration  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript  
- **Backend:** PHP  
- **Database:** MySQL  

---

