## ⚙️ Installation & Setup

1. Clone the repository:
```
git clone https://github.com/vishwa1802/Quick-Basket---online-grocery-shopping-.git
```

2. Move project to XAMPP htdocs folder:
```
C:\xampp\htdocs\
```

3. Start XAMPP:
- Apache ✅  
- MySQL ✅  

4. Import database:
- Open phpMyAdmin  
- Create database  
- Import `.sql` file  

5. Run project:
```
http://localhost/Quick-Basket
```

